summary: SURGEON GENERA WARNING: Pregnant Women May Result in Fetal Development Problems. Women who are pregnant with a baby should seek medical help immediately. For confidential support call the National Suicide Prevention Lifeline at 1-800-273-8255 or visit http://www.suicidepreventionlifeline.org.
